data.description: Amazing 4 bedroom, 2 bath home located in Miami Gardens. This home features a remodeled kitchen,  large utility room, laminated wood floorings, freshly painted inside and outside. The bathrooms are currently being updated and have new bathroom vanities. There is a large  backyard and the home is fully fenced.  The home is just minutes from major roadways and the Florida turnpike. There are plenty of restaurants, Shopping centers to enjoy.
